WITH steps AS (
  SELECT x, POW(10, x-.01) AS bucket_left, POW(10, x+.01) AS bucket_right
  FROM UNNEST(GENERATE_ARRAY(0, 3.5, .02)) AS x
), 

-- Get all the pt data.
pt AS (
  SELECT ARRAY_REVERSE(raw.Download.ServerMeasurements)[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].TCPInfo AS tcpinfo, 
    metadata.Value AS session_id, 
  FROM `mlab-oti.raw_pt.ndt7`, UNNEST (raw.Download.ClientMetadata) AS metadata
  WHERE date BETWEEN "${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}" AND "${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}"
  AND raw.Download is not NULL 
  AND ARRAY_LENGTH(raw.Download.ServerMeasurements) > 0
  AND metadata.Name = "client_session_id"
),

-- Select only ndt7 tests with matching pt tests.
ndt7 AS (
  SELECT ARRAY_REVERSE(raw.Download.ServerMeasurements)[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].TCPInfo AS tcpinfo, 
    "Full length" AS test_type,
  FROM `mlab-oti.ndt.ndt7`, UNNEST (raw.Download.ClientMetadata) AS metadata
  WHERE date BETWEEN "${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}" AND "${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}"
  AND raw.Download is not NULL 
  AND ARRAY_LENGTH(raw.Download.ServerMeasurements) > 0
  AND metadata.Name = "client_session_id"
  AND metadata.Value IN (SELECT session_id FROM pt)
),

pdf_sort AS (
  SELECT bucket_left, bucket_right, test_type, IF((SAFE_DIVIDE(tcpinfo.BytesAcked*8,tcpinfo.ElapsedTime)) BETWEEN bucket_left AND bucket_right, 1, 0) AS present_true
  FROM ndt7, steps
), pdf_totals AS (  
  SELECT bucket_left AS buckets, test_type, sum(present_true) AS total_true
  FROM   pdf_sort
  GROUP BY bucket_left, test_type
  ORDER BY bucket_left
), pdf_product  AS (
  SELECT
    total_true,
    test_type,
    trunc(buckets,2) as buckets,
    total_true AS product_true,
  FROM pdf_totals
  ORDER BY buckets
), pdf_normalized AS (
  SELECT  
    buckets,
    test_type,
    product_true / SUM(product_true) OVER (partition BY test_type) AS normalized,
    
  FROM pdf_product
  ORDER BY buckets
)
SELECT
  buckets,
  normalized,
  test_type,

FROM pdf_normalized

    total_true AS product_true,

WITH steps AS (
  SELECT x, POW(10, x-.01) AS bucket_left, POW(10, x+.01) AS bucket_right
  FROM UNNEST(GENERATE_ARRAY(0, 3.5, .02)) AS x
), 

-- Select only pt tests with matching ndt7 tests.
pt AS (
  SELECT ARRAY_REVERSE(raw.Download.ServerMeasurements)[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].TCPInfo AS tcpinfo, 
    metadata.Value AS session_id, 
    CASE
      WHEN ("max_cwnd_gain" IN (SELECT metadata.Name FROM UNNEST(raw.Download.ClientMetadata) AS metadata)) AND ("early_exit" IN (SELECT metadata.Name FROM UNNEST(raw.Download.ClientMetadata) AS metadata)) THEN "BBR and 50MB"
      WHEN ("max_cwnd_gain" IN (SELECT metadata.Name FROM UNNEST(raw.Download.ClientMetadata) AS metadata)) AND ("max_elapsed_time" IN (SELECT metadata.Name FROM UNNEST(raw.Download.ClientMetadata) AS metadata)) THEN "BBR and 5s"
      WHEN ("early_exit" IN (SELECT metadata.Name FROM UNNEST(raw.Download.ClientMetadata) AS metadata)) THEN "50MB"
      WHEN ("max_elapsed_time" IN (SELECT metadata.Name FROM UNNEST(raw.Download.ClientMetadata) AS metadata)) THEN "5s"
      ELSE "BBR"      
  END AS test_type,
  FROM `mlab-oti.raw_pt.ndt7`, UNNEST (raw.Download.ClientMetadata) AS metadata
  WHERE date BETWEEN "${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}" AND "${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}"
  AND raw.Download is not NULL 
  AND ARRAY_LENGTH(raw.Download.ServerMeasurements) > 0
  AND "client_session_id" IN (SELECT metadata.Name FROM UNNEST(raw.Download.ClientMetadata) AS metadata)
),

pdf_sort AS (
  SELECT bucket_left, bucket_right, test_type, IF((SAFE_DIVIDE(tcpinfo.BytesAcked*8,tcpinfo.ElapsedTime)) BETWEEN bucket_left AND bucket_right, 1, 0) AS present_true
  FROM pt, steps
), pdf_totals AS (  
  SELECT bucket_left AS buckets, test_type, sum(present_true) AS total_true
  FROM   pdf_sort
  GROUP BY bucket_left, test_type
  ORDER BY bucket_left
), pdf_product  AS (
  SELECT
    total_true,
    test_type,
    trunc(buckets,2) as buckets,
    total_true AS product_true,
  FROM pdf_totals
  ORDER BY buckets
), pdf_normalized AS (
  SELECT  
    buckets,
    test_type,
    product_true / SUM(product_true) OVER (partition BY test_type) AS normalized,
    
  FROM pdf_product
  ORDER BY buckets
)
SELECT
  buckets,
  normalized,
  test_type,

FROM pdf_normalized

targets.rawSql:
SELECT m.Bandwidth 
FROM `raw_pt.pair1`, UNNEST(raw.Measurements) AS m
WHERE date between "${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}" and "${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}"
AND m.Packets[SAFE_OFFSET(0)].Gap = 0

SELECT CAST(p.Size AS string) As size, (COUNT(*)/(SUM(COUNT(*)) OVER())) * 100 AS Percent
FROM `raw_pt.pair1`, UNNEST(raw.Measurements) AS m, UNNEST(m.Packets) AS p
WHERE date between "${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}" and "${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}"
GROUP BY size
ORDER BY Percent

SELECT AVG(m.Bandwidth) AS avg_bandwidth, CAST(p.Size AS string) As size_bytes
FROM `raw_pt.pair1`, UNNEST(raw.Measurements) AS m, UNNEST(m.Packets) AS p
WHERE date between "${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}" and "${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}"
GROUP BY size_bytes

SELECT p.Gap AS Gap, (COUNT(*)/(SUM(COUNT(*)) OVER())) * 100 AS Percent
FROM `raw_pt.pair1`, UNNEST(raw.Measurements) AS m, UNNEST(m.Packets) AS p
WHERE date between "${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}" and "${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}"
AND gap IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY Gap

SELECT AVG(m.Bandwidth) AS avg_bandwidth, CAST(p.Gap AS string) As gap_usecs
FROM `raw_pt.pair1`, UNNEST(raw.Measurements) AS m, UNNEST(m.Packets) AS p
WHERE date between "${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}" and "${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}"
GROUP BY gap_usecs

SELECT m.Bandwidth 
FROM `raw_pt.train1`, UNNEST(raw.Measurements) AS m
WHERE date between "${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}" and "${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}"

SELECT CAST(p.Size AS string) As size, (COUNT(*)/(SUM(COUNT(*)) OVER())) * 100 AS Percent
FROM `raw_pt.train1`, UNNEST(raw.Measurements) AS m, UNNEST(m.Packets) AS p
WHERE date between "${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}" and "${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}"
GROUP BY size
ORDER BY Percent

SELECT p.Gap AS Gap, (COUNT(*)/(SUM(COUNT(*)) OVER())) * 100 AS Percent
FROM `raw_pt.train1`, UNNEST(raw.Measurements) AS m, UNNEST(m.Packets) AS p
WHERE date between "${__from:date:YYYY-MM-DD}" and "${__to:date:YYYY-MM-DD}"
AND gap IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY Gap
